insert into posts (scheduled_at, pillar, series, format, hook, body, cta, repurpose, status) values ('2026-08-03T04:30:00.000Z', 'book', 'Broke Chronicles Monday', 'text', 'My brother Dante was my first audience.
He heard every broadcast I ever gave — years before a camera did.', 'Before Citizen TV, before Urban News, before 2M viewers, there was a boy performing news bulletins to his brother in a mud house in Lugari. I interviewed chickens. I reported droughts from the doorway. Dante clapped anyway. Here is what I know about audiences now that I did not know then: the size never mattered. The habit did. I practised being watchable for a decade before anyone watched. That is the part the overnight-success story always deletes.', 'Who was your first audience? Name them in the comments.', 'Newsletter: "practise in the dark" — the 10-year overnight success timeline, dated.', 'draft');
